\fs36 Installing
\fs24 \
To install mc.usb, you just need to drop 
\f1\b mc.usb.mxo/mxe
\f0\b0  into your Max externals folder.  The help file 
\f1\b mc.usb.help
\f0\b0  goes in your Max help folder.  You can drop the Make Controller Examples directory into the 
\f1\b patches->extras
\f0\b0  directory in your Max installation to have the examples available to you under the 
\f1\b extras
\f0\b0  menu within Max.\
\
File                                               OS X Location                                                         Windows Location\
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\

\f1\b mc.usb.mxo/mxe
\f0\b0                       [your Max 4.6 install]/Cycling '74/externals\

\f1\b mc.usb.help
\f0\b0                                 [your Max 4.6 install]/max-help\

\f1\b Make Controller Examples
